{"tid":1186748,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有請小鳳姐] 環亞體檢結業 有內地人要求退款不果並報警","createTime":"2019-06-05T06:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T08:45:02.000Z","uid":44562,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"beb55dd062f29044f86a48f493ad775d56b4d27e","tid":1186748,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:46:17.000Z","msg":"環亞體檢集團有限公司宣布結業，其中在佐敦的辦事處外貼出清盤結業的通告。早上有數名內地旅客，到佐敦的體檢中心了解。<br />\n<br />\n來自上海的郝小姐表示，近日收到中介通知，建議她到場退款，她昨晚抵港，早上到場才知公司結業。她說已支付約6000元，只接種了一針HPV九價預防疫苗，早上已就事件報警，但擔心內地人難以在港追討賠償。<br />\n<br />\n另一名來自深圳的王小姐說，她們約12人早前購買了HPV疫苗療程，共涉及約7萬元。她說自從該公司早前被指疫苗出問題後，她感到擔心，趁今日來港購物時順道退款，到場才知公司結業。她又說，因不熟悉香港有何追討途徑，不知如何處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%92%B0%E4%BA%9E%E9%AB%94%E6%AA%A2%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD-%E6%9C%89%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E9%80%80%E6%AC%BE%E4%B8%8D%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%A6%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6-041628480.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E4%25BA%259E%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E9%2580%2580%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%259E%259C%25E4%25B8%25A6%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6-041628480.html&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKLx68f20TVEdZexmFDfnZHo4%3D&h=2891a204\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%92%B0%E4%BA%9E%E9%AB%94%E6%AA%A2%E7%B5%90%E6%A5%AD-%E6%9C%89%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E9%80%80%E6%AC%BE%E4%B8%8D%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%A6%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6-041628480.html</a>"},{"pid":"1f407949161931bc7f067f1a03be84e547663d4e","tid":1186748,"uid":997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:47:05.000Z","msg":"執左笠仲想退錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a365aef908ec5ec4433e02fd8e0e6938fa34c0b2","tid":1186748,"uid":37502,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:48:11.000Z","msg":"搵夠水